parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident, and the lack of a functional airbag system can lead to a loss of vehicle safety and performance.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag does not deploy in an accident
the airbag deploys unnecessarily
or the airbag is faulty and needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manufacturer to provide adequate recall repairs and communication can lead to a lack of trust in the vehicle's safety and performance, and can cause inconvenience and financial loss to the vehicle owner.
symptoms: The recall repair is not completed properly
the parts are not available
or the manufacturer does not provide adequate communication about the recall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS system can cause the vehicle to swerve or drift while driving, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle tends to sway or drift while driving
especially at high speeds; the steering wheel feels loose or unresponsive; the vehicle requires constant corrections to stay on course; the steering system is over-sensitive and jerky.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning horn can lead to a loss of warning ability, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The horn stops working
only works when the steering wheel is turned to the right or left
and won't work when the wheel is straight.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag System Failure - Passenger Seat Belt Light
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning airbag system can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injuries and fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
the passenger seat belt light continuously beeps
and the dealer is unable to identify the problem.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A hot key can cause burns and discomfort, and may lead to a loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: The ignition key gets extremely hot during normal operation
making it difficult to remove from the ignition.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure - Door Lock Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning door lock system can lead to a loss of safety and security, making it difficult to exit the vehicle in an emergency.
symptoms: The electronic locks on the front doors only work sporadically
and the rear doors work as expected most of the time.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure - Window and Lock Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning window and lock system can lead to a loss of safety and security, making it difficult to exit the vehicle in an emergency.
symptoms: The windows and locks malfunction
and the trunk latch gets stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A stalling engine can lead to a loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls without warning
and the failure recurs on multiple occasions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can lead to a loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle speeds up without warning
and the gas pedal does not react to foot input.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure - Radio and Airbag Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning electrical system can lead to a loss of safety and security, and may cause accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The radio fails to function
and a rodent breach causes damage to wires and electrical components
including the airbag system.
